Information needed to process MultiTab and then continue with normal dispatching for the underlying technology.

Parameters:
fullUrl - The full path, including query parameters. Will be used to assert that we aren't redirecting to the same URL (and therefore infinite loop) in the locked case.
request - A generic request object.
response - A generic response object.
